From da0fae0b314b4ba7dcf2ee17c878a670a7a97053 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: lutong <lutong14@huawei.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 22:37:14 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2/4] mm/hugetlb: add HugeTLB anonymous page swap support

Add CONFIG_HUGETLB_SWAP with core swap-accounting scaffolding,
swap_duplicate_nr() for contiguous swap entries, and implement
anonymous HugeTLB page swap-out/swap-in with LRU management,
etmem integration, and vmscan reclaim handling.

Signed-off-by: nashzhou <zhouhaipeng13@huawei.com>
---
